-- Pemex Reserves Gain for 1st Time Since at Least 2000
-- B y   C a r l o s   M a n u e l   R o d r i g u e z
-- 2012-02-28T19:12:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-28/pemex-reserves-gain-for-1st-time-since-at-least-2000-correct-.html
(Corrects timing of reserve losses in first paragraph.)  Petroleos Mexicanos,  Latin America ’s
largest oil producer, posted a gain in its proven reserves for
the first time since at least 2000 boosting the country’s
replacement rate to 101.1 percent, said  Carlos Morales , Pemex’s
head of exploration and production.  To contact the reporter on this story:
